{"tid":2207221,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"蘋果日報：香港大學2名實驗室員工初步確診！","createTime":"2020-09-18T04:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T06:52:05.000Z","uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1183199194b03f3c2a23b994153e12077d7381f9","tid":2207221,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T04:35:35.000Z","msg":"本港疫情持續緩和，據悉，今日（18日）錄得約3宗確診個案，當中兩宗為本地個案，均與之前個案有關連，另一宗為輸入個案，由於預料沒有源頭不明個案，衞生署今日或不舉行疫情記者會。另據知昨晚有2宗初步確診個案為是港大員工，有指兩人在實驗室工作，已在瑪麗醫院留醫。<br />\n昨日（17日）則錄得9宗確診個案，當中6宗屬本地感染，其中一半個案源頭不明；其餘3宗與其他個案有關，包括一人是大圍交通城群組的家人，該群組累計有15人確診。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200918/AKTUAJYK5FAADEV66QJ3ABQPPQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200918%2FAKTUAJYK5FAADEV66QJ3ABQPPQ%2F&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=7ec4d5a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200918%2FAKTUAJYK5FAADEV66QJ3ABQPPQ%2F&h=63eaa30d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200918/AKTUAJYK5FAADEV66QJ3ABQPPQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f640d30730232279fcea27f1729f6fcdec3b4fb","tid":2207221,"uid":223360,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T04:42:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />實驗室員工。之前ust都係咁講，其實係住大埔仔嘅大陸post doc。"},{"pid":"855bd88d3a92d7081b0a9ee07a02bb48be4df251","tid":2207221,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T05:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82583287e490562c1f24747e7450d991bb4dddc","tid":2207221,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"